import React from 'react'
import { NavLink } from 'react-router-dom'
import { AppBar, Toolbar, Typography, Button } from '@material-ui/core'

const NavBar = () => {
    return (
        <AppBar variant="static">
            <Toolbar>
                <Typography variant="h5" color="inherit">
                    The Calorie Police
                </Typography>
                        <Button color="inherit"><NavLink textDecoration="none" to="/">Minhas informações</NavLink></Button>
                        <Button color="inherit"><NavLink to="/food">Minha dieta</NavLink></Button> 
            </Toolbar>
        </AppBar>
    )
}

export default NavBar
